Subject: [PATCH 3/3] fix frontend runtime crashes and bring test suite to
 181/181

runtime fixes:
- default overlays={} in MapContainer and OverlayPanel so components
  don't crash when prop is omitted (was breaking 4 tests and a real
  edge case on first render)
- render WeatherSelector preset details as a single text node so it
  is queryable and doesn't produce React hydration warnings

test fixes:
- add useMap and Popup to react-map-gl mock (EquityLayer and StagingPins
  popup use them; missing exports caused all App tests to fail)
- update LayerToggle test: component now has 4 layers not 3 (EMS Stations added)
- update WeatherSelector test: preset values changed (22/10/4 deg, 0/4/12mm)
- update CoverageBars test: labels renamed to Without/With FirstWave
- update StagingPins test: component now renders zone pills + ambulance
  dots rather than emoji markers
- wrap MapContainer test in QueryClientProvider (EquityLayer uses react-query)
- update ImpactPanel test: EquityChart is not rendered by ImpactPanel;
  assert on OverlayPanel content instead
- update App test: disambiguate ambulance count from staging pin badges,
  account for 5th role=checkbox from OverlayPanel div
